\'s history? <a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/history-of-the-iwdpa/\">Visit our History page.</a>\r\n\r\nWant to read the IWDPA constitution? <a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/membership/\">Visit our Membership page.</a>\r\n\r\nWant to review scholarship and publications about freestanding academic units? <a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/scholarship-research/\">Visit our Scholarship page.</a>\r\n\r\nReview past agendas and meeting minutes on our <a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/archive/\">Archive page</a>.','About','','inherit','closed','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2015-07-29 01:22:33','2015-07-29 01:22:33','',5,'http://independentwriting.org/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(4119,1,'2015-07-29 01:22:50','2015-07-29 01:22:50','Past artifacts and documents related to our organization are here.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2012-CCCC-Meeting-Minutes-Final.docx\">2012--CCCC Meeting Minutes Final</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2013-CCCC-Meeting-Agenda.pptx\">2013 CCCC Meeting Agenda</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2014-CCC-Meeting-Minutes.docx\">2014--CCC Meeting Minutes</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2014-WPA-Meeting-Minutes.docx\">2014--WPA Meeting Minutes</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2015-CCCC-Meeting-Minutes.docx\">2015--CCCC Meeting Minutes</a>','Archive','','inherit','closed','open','','4110-revision-v1','','','2015-07-29 01:22:50','2015-07-29 01:22:50','',4110,'http://independentwriting.org/4110-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(4120,1,'2015-07-29 01:23:39','2015-07-29 01:23:39','Past artifacts and documents related to our organization are here.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://independentwriting.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2015-CCCC-Meeting-Minutes.docx\">2015--CCCC Meeting Minutes</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http